text: Bogdanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Bogdanovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 474 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Bogdanovo, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
